{"tid":764432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 一批工人鰂魚涌地盤示威 指分判商拖欠約271萬元薪金","createTime":"2018-08-02T03:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T05:44:41.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4ffa2c9232dd340459e9cf84624a69706a48c07c","tid":764432,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T03:46:42.000Z","msg":"一批工人到鰂魚涌一個地盤示威，指分判商拖欠約50名冷氣水電工兩個月薪金。  三十多名工人與職工盟代表，到太古坊地盤外示威，工人聲稱被分判商拖欠6月及7月的薪金及加班費等，合共約271萬元。  有工人指曾向分判商及大判、二判等追薪，並向勞工處求助，但仍然未能解決事件。  在示威期間，二判商高砂派人到場，指會於數日後發出薪金，獲工人初步接納。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5b627752e603831e06e936b4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5b627752e603831e06e936b4%2F&d=TlYb0R5tA8yi7HBAaSqlrDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=a81f2760\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5b627752e603831e06e936b4/</a>"},{"pid":"644b5b19e3542813b8c07058465c136a2d320e17","tid":764432,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T03:47:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/114701_b9750b2c2bf01283e7142afa1c631504.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F114701_b9750b2c2bf01283e7142afa1c631504.png&h=4361a84a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/114702_16ebf8479a863d52778a0522ba8db8e0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F114702_16ebf8479a863d52778a0522ba8db8e0.png&h=e8cc8439&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/114703_44391659266180bd3ef8bc62bec1199a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F114703_44391659266180bd3ef8bc62bec1199a.png&h=d04f0086&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/114704_12a645e72d079022bdf2ebce46d78b2